data.description: ** Assumable 3.1% Loan Call me for more details ***Nestled in the heart of Tooele, this enchanting single family bungalow cottage exudes timeless charm. Boasting 4 bedrooms, 2 baths and a versatile bonus room, the home effortlessly combines comfort with functionality. The well-appointed kitchen comes complete with appliances, ensuring modern convenience for your culinary endeavors.  Outside, a welcoming carport and a 1 car-garage provide convenient parking options, while a storage shed adds practicality to meet you storage needs. The character of this home extends beyond its walls, as it sits in the midst of the vibrant community in Tooele, offering a lifestyle that seamlessly blends urban amenities with suburban tranquility. Experience the warmth of a true family home, where every detail contributes to its charm.This residence invites you to embrace a lifestyle that modern comfort with the nostalgic appeal of a classic bungalow cottage. Welcome to the heart of Tooele, where this delightful property awaits its next chapter.
